                        类型            默认设备
System.in   标准输入    InputStream     键盘
System.out  标准输出    PrintStream     显示器

System.in:public static final InputStream in = null;
        编译类型：InputStream
        运行类型：System.in.getClass():BufferedInputStream


System.out:public static final PrintStream out = null;
        编译类型：PrintStream
        运行类型：PrintStream
